Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 04 of Thoracic CT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Mediastinum' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Mediastinal shift' radio button is enabled
And 'Mediastinal widening' radio button is enabled
And 'Pneumomediastinum' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Mediastinal shift' radio button
Then 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Mediastinal widening' radio button
Then 'Upper mediastinum' checkbox is enabled
And 'Lower mediastinum' checkbox is enabled
